# NOTE (2026-04-27): the entire .claude/ directory IS intentionally tracked
# in this repo (per Pardha — sync trust rules + PDLC run artifacts + agents
# across machines). Nothing under .claude/ should be ignored.
#
# TODO: revisit before any public publish or before adding collaborators —
# settings.local.json may contain machine-specific paths and PDLC run folders
# may contain in-progress drafts not meant for an external audience. To
# selectively ignore at that point:
#   .claude/settings.local.json   # if you want machine-local trust only
#   .claude/pdlc-runs/            # if you don't want to share run artifacts
# Then `git rm -r --cached .claude/<path>` to remove from index.
